Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:44.84,Ending2 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}Is there anyone who has a dream these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:48.47,Ending2 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}I've grown tired of that line
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.68,Ending2 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}I'd planned to walk the whole way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:55.72,Ending2 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}Recently, even the sky has become empty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:59.64,Ending2 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}"I want to see you," and, "I was watching you"
